### Branch 3 — Abyssal Breaker

*Focus: Demon knight, corruption as Armour stripper, Armour Break stacking, spell damage explosion capstone*

The knight becomes a Demon and a living corruption engine. Every corruption stack strips enemy Armour. The knight applies corruption on every attack including to the enemy hero. T2 splits into spell burst or demon aggression paths. The capstone detonates accumulated Armour Break as spell damage on enemy death.

|Tier|ID                 |Name               |Effect                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|----|-------------------|-------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|T0  |corrupting_presence|Corrupting Presence|Abyssal Knight’s race becomes Demon. Each stack of Corruption on an enemy also reduces that enemy’s Armour by 100                                                                                                                                                                    |
|T1  |abyssal_strike     |Abyssal Strike     |Whenever Abyssal Knight attacks any target (minion or enemy hero), apply 1 Corruption stack to that target                                                                                                                                                                           |
|T2  |breaker_path       |Breaker’s Path     |Choose one permanently: **Path of Ruination** — your spells apply 1 Corruption stack to their target on cast; each Corruption stack on a target increases spell damage it takes by 100. **Path of Destruction** — friendly Demon attacks apply 50 Armour Break to their attack target|
|T3  |armour_explosion   |Armour Explosion   |CAPSTONE: When an enemy minion dies, deal spell damage to all enemies equal to that minion’s total accumulated Armour Break value                                                                                                                                                    |

**Key interactions:**

- T0 + T1: knight attacks simultaneously deal damage, apply corruption, and strip 100 Armour per stack — two debuff systems from one attack
- Path of Ruination + T3: corruption stacks on surviving enemies increase spell damage taken, amplifying the explosion damage they receive
- Path of Destruction + T3: demon attacks build Armour Break directly, feeding the explosion value
- T3 explosion is spell damage — bypasses Armour on all targets hit, benefits from Path of Ruination’s corruption amplification
- Branch wants a demon-heavy or spell-heavy deck depending on T2 path chosen

